cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.CY 

The paper discusses the use of wireless communication and sensing devices in vehicles for traffic control applications, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed method involves processing data using on-line traffic simulation technique, which can be categorized under control systems (cs.SY) and information theory (cs.IT). Additionally, the paper discusses the application of the proposed method in different types of traffic control systems, which can be classified under cybernetics (cs.CY).
